title: Echoes of Nature - Morning Songbirds
description:
Echoes of Nature - Morning Songbirds


This disc contains seven tracks of natural sounds of the wild for a total of 46 minutes of delicate listening. The only non-bird sounds are surf, rain, wind and a babbling stream. The recordings are remarkably clear.
